            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Calm."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " For all things, there is a tide. I set sail when it is right, and mend my nets when it is not. (Lawful)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Windblown."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I go where the winds blow. No man or woman tells me where or when to sail. (Chaotic)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "3"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Aspiring."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I will gain the favor of a Zor or Zora patron, maybe even one of the Blades! (Any)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Salty."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I want people to look to me as an expert on plying Mulmaster Harbor. (Any)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Selfless."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " We are all children of the sea. I help everyone in peril afloat and ashore. (Good)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Let them Drown."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I refuse to risk my hide to help others. They wouldn't help me if roles were reversed. (Evil)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
